data.description: Have you ever seen a listing that shared an automated valuation with you? Look at photo #2! That is without the new appliances and hardwood floors! Tired of fighting with Santa, price improved!!!!  Welcome to an exceptional real estate opportunity in the heart of the vibrant Portland, Oregon.  Prime Location Awaits You: Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, this property offers the perfect balance of seclusion and accessibility. It's a stone's throw from major freeways, yet it has a generous cul-de-sac setting that is nearly triple the average size! This provides a serene and private atmosphere to live in! This is more than a home; it's a retreat in the midst of a bustling area.**RV Parking and Ample Garage Space: For the adventure enthusiasts, the property boasts extensive RV parking and storage options. The spacious two-car garage, deeper than standard, is not just for parking; it features a convenient door leading to the backyard, blending functionality with ease.**Step Inside to Modern Elegance: Prepare to be awed as you enter a space that feels brand new. The home has been meticulously upgraded, boasting completely refinished hardwood floors throughout, giving it a timeless elegance.  The heart of this home is its kitchen, equipped with BRAND NEW stainless appliances. This includes a 45db whisper-quiet dishwasher, an easy-to-clean glass top stove/oven, and a sleek microwave oven. A brand-new, high-quality refrigerator completes this modern culinary space.  Windows and Furnace? The best in comfort: Experience tranquility and efficiency with Milgard Windows double-pane vinyl windows and a brand-new Lennox gas furnace.  The local court trustee, having completed probate, ensures a smooth and swift transaction. A quick close is not just possible; it's promised, with assistance readily available for your buyer.
